text: Paraphryneta guttata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Quedenfeldt in 1888, originally under the genus Inesida.BioLib.cz - Paraphryneta guttata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1888
title: Paraphryneta guttata
